I'm not able to reproduce this on the 0.10.0 TF binary release. Could it be possible that you've made local source modifications?

The intended behavior is indeed to error:
`tensorflow.python.framework.errors.InvalidArgumentError: indices[10] = 10 is not in [0, 10)
     [[Node: embedding_lookup_1 = Gather[Tindices=DT_INT32, Tparams=DT_FLOAT, _class=["loc:@Placeholder_2"], validate_indices=true, _device="/job:localhost/replica:0/task:0/cpu:0"](_recv_Placeholder_2_0, _recv_Placeholder_3_0)]]
